    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve truly babied it since day one! It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously maintained, this is definitely the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 45900.0,
