    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal engineering. Powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, the engine features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band and a 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a limited-slip Variable M Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. This example is mechanically flawless: the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural lateral rigidity, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension retains factory-spec damping with no bushing deflection, preserving the communicative steering rack's precision. Finished in a concours-level exterior with zero oxidation, this is an investment-grade specimen of Bavarian performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
